```
On this page:

- Change password to Client Portal 
- Log in to Client Portal with an email address
- Changing email contact addresses
- Editing Personal Information
```

Login to Client portal at http://ServerpointAPPS.com and click on **MENU** on left top >> Click on **Edit your profile**.

```diagram

```



**Change password to Client Portal**

Customer can change their client portal password. To do that go to **Edit your profile** and complete the form under **Change password to Client Portal** with old and new password and then submit the form.

```diagram

```

For Web hosting account

> Be aware that, for web hosting account this will also change the password to log in to the server via FTP, SFTP, etc
{.is-info}

**Log in to Client Portal with an email address**

Now customer can log in to client portal with an email address instead of his account name. Password should be same as the client portal password. 

To add email address go to **Edit your profile** and write the email address under **Log in to Client Portal with an email address** and save it

```diagram

```

**Changing email contact addresses**

Customer can add total 4 email addresses

- 2 email address for technical issues
- 2 email address for billing issues

```diagram

```

**Editing Personal Information**

Customer can also update their address information from client portal. Go to **Edit your personal contact information** and modify/add address.
